title: Miscarriage: The Good, The Bad, The Ugly | Ep. 3
itunes:author: Yeah No I Know, Jenna, Brooklin & Kristen Leanne
description: 1 out of every 4 women experiences a miscarriage (in our case, 2 out of 3!). It's WAY more common than you think. This topic is somewhat taboo, but not here. Today we're talking about two of our miscarriage experiences, both completely different than the other. We are also answering YOUR questions on the subject: what to say to someone who has had a miscarriage, how to be there for them, what to expect, when can you start trying again?
